N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 226.8 - Violations

State Regulations
A violation of any of the rules set forth in this Part shall
be referred to the Attorney General, Department of Financial Services and/or
any other appropriate law enforcement or regulatory entity for
action. Notes
